data.description: Nestled in the desirable Litchfield Neighborhood, this brick home offers a spacious floor plan and recently painted interior. The property features a sizable living room with a fireplace and a formal dining room. The kitchen offers recessed lighting, granite countertops, an island, and a breakfast nook surrounded by windows. The primary bedroom with coffered ceilings features a walk-in closet, as well as an ensuite with a shower, bathtub, and dual vanities. The covered patio makes for a cozy place to unwind in the evenings. With a premiere location in the Jenks  School District near Jenks Riverwalk, Tulsa Hills, new outlet mall and entertainment, this home is a Must See! Short drive to Creek Turnpike and HWY 75. Pre-inspections performed, repair invoice available.
